des: You're stuck, and there's no one left! Quick, gather the cookies and... oh, you don't feel so good. Plot: An inspiring inventor accidentally let his creations out of his garage, and you're the only one left! How to play: Test your memory by remembering details about parts of the story. Answer at least 5 questions correctly to win! Future update information: Parts of the story may be changed, added, or removed because of story inspiration and/or user feedback for a longer, more satisfying gameplay experience.
